description: Xinliwang International Holdings Company Ltd., an energy technology company, designs and develops clean and practical power and energy solutions. The company offers flowing electrolyte direct methanol fuel cell for various applications, including stationary power generation, portable applications, and transportation. It also focuses on developing and marketing hybrid power systems, fuel cell battery, and related technologies. The company was formerly known as SymPowerco Corporation and changed its name to Xinliwang International Holdings Company Ltd. in April 2019. Xinliwang International Holdings Company Ltd. was incorporated in 1970 and is based in Gardnerville, Nevada.
